states above the potential.

89
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,650
And we'll have a discrete
set of bound states--

90
00:03:54,650 --> 00:03:57,000
Probably, it's reasonable
to expect some finite number

91
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,416
