00:05:18,460 --> 00:05:20,749
We know how to solve for
the energy eigenfunctions

122
00:05:20,749 --> 00:05:22,040
when the potential is constant.

123
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,498
What are the energy
eigenfunctions?

