00:09:24,629 --> 00:09:25,670
So this is discontinuous.

230
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:30,900

231
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:32,960
Phi prime of x,
however, is the integral

232
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:35,627
